comments: Reddish (ATL) maintains legal position along Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Howard (LAL) briefly grasps Len's (ATL) jersey during the rebound.
Len (ATL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Len (ATL) and Howard (LAL) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Davis (LAL) cleanly dislodges the ball during Young's (ATL) driving shot attempt.
Parker (ATL) initiates contact with Davis' (LAL) arm after Davis gathers the rebound and the contact affects his SQBR.
Len (ATL) establishes a legal position in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Replay review of the foul called on Parker (ATL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.
Hunter (ATL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hunter (ATL) makes incidental contact with Davis' (LAL) wrist after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Replay review of the foul called on Davis (LAL) pursuant to a coachs challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Hunter (ATL) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Carter (ATL) makes marginal contact with Green (LAL) as he disengages from the contact during the inbound.
Len (ATL) establishes a legal position in Caruso's (LAL) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Green (LAL) and Carter (ATL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Carter (ATL) commits a take foul on Green (LAL).
Green (LAL) makes marginal contact with Young (ATL) at the start of his dribble.
Carter (ATL) slightly extends his arm across Jamess (LAL) body as he sets the pick in his path, but the contact does not affect his ability to defend.
